name: Key To My Heart Necklace
description: Closed sterling silver heart, hand stamped with a small font letter stamp. Accented with a freshwater pearl and a cute little key.

name: Personalized Charm Bracelet
description:
This cute sterling silver bracelet measures 7 inches in length. The sterling discs can be stamped with your choice of names, dates, words. I also added a sweet freshwater pearl but a coloured crystal can be added as well.
$25.00 - Bracelet 
~ each disc is $5.00

name: Rectangle Pendant Tags
description:
These rectangle tag pendants are the latest addition to my sterling silver collection. They are the same size as the other tags, except these have a tube at the top of them which I soldered and added a large ring for a more beautiful effect. It is then accented with a pretty 6mm taupe color swarovski crystal. 
These tags can be hand stamped with names, dates, or favorite inspirational saying. You have the choice of a swarovski crystal or freshwater pearl. This necklace also comes complete with a 16", 18", or 20" sterling silver ball chain.

name: Sterling Silver Teardrop
description: Sterling silver teardrop pendant is hand stamped in a small font with names. Words or dates can also be stamped. Comes complete with a 18" sterling silver ball chain.

name: Open Circle "Mommy Medal"
description:
By far my most popular!! 
This 1.5 inch open circle sterling silver pendant can fit up to four names comfortable. It is accented with a freshwater pearl and strung on a 16, 18, or 20 inch sterling ball chain.
